@startuml
' @id(USE-SESSION-BRIEF)
' @desc(USE-SESSION-BRIEF, "Implemented: `mdd context` (mdd-cli Commands::Context) calls Project::session_context, which builds the whole-map TOC (map_toc over .mdd/map) and folds in the map_status freshness verdict. mdd init wires it as a Claude Code SessionStart hook in .claude/settings.json (Project::write_session_hook). Realized by SEQ-SESSION-BRIEF; owned by CMP-SESSION-CLI + CMP-INIT-HOOK.")
' @id(USE-DIAGRAMS-FIRST)
' @desc(USE-DIAGRAMS-FIRST, "Implemented as the diagrams-first reading-order text in templates::claude_entrypoint / agents_entrypoint (injected into CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md managed blocks by mdd init): fresh -> read + follow source_links / stale -> /mdd-map the drifted area first. The AGENTS variant tells Codex to run `mdd context` manually. Realized by SEQ-DIAGRAMS-FIRST; owned by CMP-ENTRYPOINT-DIRECTIVE.")
